{"tid":1786901,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"天道好還 - 陳也","createTime":"2019-12-17T13:34:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T13:35:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0fd13ebfd5f2ac878dd7f656c94ae5ce4ad7b46e","tid":1786901,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T13:34:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20191217/20826268/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191217%2F20826268%2F&d=oGSqBYpvdEZZERTBUGrA0pKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=c78afeb7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191217%2F20826268%2F&h=e7bfaf08\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20191217/20826268/</a><br />\n<br />\n天道好還 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191217/large/1576485415_8c59.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191217%2Flarge%2F1576485415_8c59.jpg&h=20e26f02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n家訂&times;匯報，真金白銀，睇完頭版，有助逆線思維。<br />\n<br />\n像早兩日，全版公告，恐襲籠罩聖誕，市道民心滿佈陰霾咁話。內頁就有草「管」人命的警謊代表，介紹屯門搜捕得來的遙控炸彈，那套架生，內行人才明。但豬嘴模式，咦，唔係阿塗畫的「贏」字式樣，從未見過小朋友穿戴，這樣的文具，哪裏搵？唔，警力OT自然搵得到。炸彈呢，據報還是跟華仁後山找到的不相同。黑警做嘢，唔使你教，插贓呢瓣，駕輕就熟。當羅致光認為「社會無可能愈扶愈貧」，我們也有理由相信「炸藥無可能愈搵愈pro」，唯一解釋，又係嗰句，黑警做嘢，唔使你教，九億五的補水，無爭議硬袋。<br />\n<br />\n黑警開槍發大財，被頭版害到一頸血的零售飲食小商戶硬啃，冇仇報。藍店更閉翳，睇住頭條悶喊「人地嚟支持你地害死人！」、「醒啲好唔好？」被執笠前的悲鳴，黑警四萬咁口拍住玻璃朱一批二打六奀星舉心心手勢，睬你藍店都戇。1.1萬拎到9.5億補水的TG警，過深圳飽食海底撈，唔吼本地二噁英BBQ，跟埋劉蛇去中山買警樓，香港經濟，黑警冇扶，幾難唔貧啊張司長！庚子將至，官逼貧反，天道好還！ <br />\n<br />\n陳也<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"2922ae8255e1fc8c53fdfabbe65bf4f13bb30cd7","tid":1786901,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T13:35:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cMC8VCF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcMC8VCF.jpg&h=36102201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-sin2-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/79171653_153614429381900_7842117770006233088_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_oc=AQmucP1kby-cRITxgOACmF7RLYKzS6mhC3XxyWj80ckb-U-hZ0QLjDM4FkacBa8he0c&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-sin2-2.xx&amp;oh=f485126eda1dc3e8f819bf943c798b1a&amp;oe=5EAED219\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-sin2-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F79171653_153614429381900_7842117770006233088_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26_nc_oc%3DAQmucP1kby-cRITxgOACmF7RLYKzS6mhC3XxyWj80ckb-U-hZ0QLjDM4FkacBa8he0c%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-sin2-2.xx%26oh%3Df485126eda1dc3e8f819bf943c798b1a%26oe%3D5EAED219&h=70a59658&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sdw2RCH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsdw2RCH.jpg&h=8da8b8c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NTntx6h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNTntx6h.jpg&h=228c1213&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}